Spent the last several years focusing on stunts and working crew on student films, but now I’m also looking to update my acting reel to better showcase my ability. Figure I might as well throw my hat out while I’m out here submitting. 😅

I have a B.A. Acting w/ minors in Stage Combat and Voiceover, and have representation. Moved from Chicago this year, have worked commercially and previously been pinned for network shows. 😊 

ChasityCoy.com

Send any audition details/sides to CoyStunts@gmail.com or DM me. 😊

Hello All! We are currently seeking 11 people to cast for a project featuring the internet sensation Sturniolo Triplets! We prefer individuals (Male) who have a similar stature to the triplets, around 5'8 ", slim, and 18 years or older, though applicants of any ethnicity are welcome.

The shoot is scheduled for Monday from 11 AM to 4 PM in West Hollywood. Although this gig is unpaid, it offers a valuable opportunity to be featured in a high-profile video, and food will be provided.

If anyone is interested, please let me know. They can contact me at campbellchae@gmail.com. Thank you!

topComments.text: Very much interested

sharedPost.text:
🎬 The Foundry Acting Studio…. Where Real Actors Are Made

Have you ever wanted to be an actor, but people told you it was impossible?
Maybe they laughed. Maybe they said, “Yeah right, you’ll be on TV one day.”
Maybe you believed them.

The truth is, it is possible. And we’re proving it every single day.

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we’ve taken people from call centres, factories, construction sites and put them on real film sets. We’ve helped ordinary people create extraordinary careers.

Because when you train with us, you’re not just joining another acting class, you’re stepping into a professional studio that’s already earned the highest recognition possible:

✨ SPOTLIGHT APPROVED – our curriculum exceeds the UK’s highest acting standard by over three times.
🌍 SAG RECOGNISED – the same union that represents every Hollywood star on earth.
🎥 FILM-FOCUSED TRAINING – you don’t just practice scenes; you act in real films. Short films, features, festival submissions, full productions we make them all in-house, to professional industry standard.

And all of this — for just £100 every 4 weeks (£80 for teens).
No false promises. No city centre price tags. Just real, legitimate training and real results.

We believe acting shouldn’t be locked behind London doors.
That’s why we’re bringing professional-level training to Yorkshire and the North, so anyone with the passion to perform can do it, whether you’re 16 or 60, starting fresh or chasing the dream you left behind.

🎭 Because the truth is: there is no other independent studio in the UK that offers what we do.
We’re Spotlight approved.
We’re SAG recognised.
We make films.
We get results.

You don’t get more legitimate than that.
You just don’t.

So, if you’re ready to stop wondering “what if” and start actually doing it, this is your moment.

🔥 SPOTLIGHT APPROVED. SAG RECOGNISED. FILM FOCUSED.
The Foundry Acting Studio….
Where impossible dreams get rehearsed, filmed, and released.

🎬 Adult & Teen Classes | 🎭 Limited Places | 🌍 Open Across Yorkshire & The North
👉 Message us now to reserve your place.

TV 2 Dokumentar søger en mandlig statist i alderen 30-40 år som er ganske "almindelig" af udseende. Det er til visualiseringsoptagelser på torsdag d. 23. oktober kl. ca. 13 til 17 i Valby til en kommende dokumentar.

Optagelserne foregår på et kontor, og statisten skal spille en kontoransat. 

Jobbet er lønnet via honorar.

Passer du ind i ovenstående beskrivelse og er interesseret i jobbet, send da en mail til nyh.casting@tv2.dk med en kort beskrivelse af dig selv, evt. tidligere jobs og et par vellignende billeder.

Facebookbeskeder og -kommentarer besvares IKKE.

🎭 Studenterrevyen 2026 søger tekstforfattere! ✍️

Elsker du at skrive sjove, skarpe eller satiriske tekster, der får folk til at grine? Så er det nu, du kan få dine ord til at leve på scenen!

Vi leder efter tekster til sketches, monologer og sange — alt fra skæv hverdagshumor og bidende satire til absurde indfald og musikalske numre. Erfaring er ikke nødvendig, bare du har noget på hjerte og en god idé.

📩 Send dine tekster (eller idéer) til forfatter@studenterrevyen.dk

sharedPost.text:
Statister søges til kortfilmen "KLAGESANG"  (ulønnet)

Hej alle sammen,

Vi er i gang med en ny kortfilm, KLAGESANG, en afgangsfilm af 18 Frames, og vi leder efter statister til nogle smukke og stemningsfulde middelalderscener i Helsingør.

Vi søger:

Nonner
Torsdag d. 23. oktober
Fredag d. 24. oktober

Riddere
Torsdag d. 23. oktober

Det hele bliver optaget i dagstimerne.

Om filmen:

Klagesang er en coming-of-age kortfilm inspireret af Hildegard von Bingens liv – en sanselig og spirituel oplysningsrejse midt i middelalderens religiøse mørke.

Vi følger den unge nonne Hilde, der får visioner gennem naturen, som hendes abbedisse tolker som guddommelige.

Da den sårede Abbas – en persisk mand på flugt fra korsfarerne – søger tilflugt i klostret, bliver Hildes tro sat på prøve, og en ny form for spiritualitet begynder at spire.

Filmen er ikke anti-religiøs, men handler om tro, tvivl og menneskelighed – og om at finde sin egen vej i mødet med en verden i forandring.

Optagelserne foregår i Helsingør

Hvis du (eller nogen du kender) kunne have lyst til at være med i et spændende og meningsfuldt filmprojekt, så skriv endelig til mig

Enten her på Facebook eller på mail: livannettemuus@outlook.dk

Læs mere om 18 frames her: https://www.18frames.dk/

MY MOMMA’S ERA: THE MUSICAL – SEEN THROUGH MY MOTHER’S LENS

Saturday, November 8, 2025
Greenwood Oasis Theater – 7621 S. Greenwood Ave, Chicago, IL
Showtime: 7 PM | VIP Experience: 4 PM | Doors Open: 6 PM
FREE PARKING

Come dressed in your best 40s, 50s, 60s, or 70s attire!
(It’s recommended — not required — for the full experience!)

Step back in time and experience a powerful musical journey through the Great Migration, Bronzeville’s rich Black history, and the soul of World War II-era Chicago — told through acting, singing, dancing, and narration.

 Featuring unforgettable portrayals of:
Billie Holiday, Nat King Cole, Ella Fitzgerald, Dinah Washington, Cab Calloway, Etta James
Plus a moving tribute to Minnie Riperton, Chicago’s own.

A dynamic cast. Real stories. Legendary music.
This is more than entertainment — it’s edutainment.

PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS — NOW SEEKING FINAL CREW MEMBERS

**We’re bringing a few more people aboard an already full production team for George Orwell’s *****1984*****, directed by M.A.C.**

We’re looking for:
* **Assistant Producer**
* **Social Media / Marketing** Manager
* **Sound Board Operator**
* **Lighting Board Operator**

Performances run **December 4–7, 2025** at **Three Stories Theater (937 Liberty Ave, Downtown Pittsburgh)**.

Our **cast and crew of over 30 artists** are already deep in rehearsals and production work, and our design team has fully built out the world of the show. We’re looking for a few final team members to join the effort and help bring this ambitious production to completion.

**ASSISTANT PRODUCER**

Supports the Executive Producer with logistics, communications, scheduling, and coordination across departments. Ideal for someone organized, proactive, and interested in hands-on producing experience in a professional theatre environment.

**SOCIAL MEDIA / MARKETING MANAGER**

Join our marketing team to help manage social channels, coordinate content posting, and support our show rollout.
We already have **two resident photographers/videographers** and a **backlog of content ready to be edited, polished, and posted**. You’ll be shaping how this production is presented to the public.

SOUND & LIGHTING BOARD OPERATORS

We have professional **sound and lighting designers** who have already built out the show’s systems and cues — we’re simply looking for **two operators** to put that design work into action during **tech week and performances**.
Experience with QLab (for Sound) or ETC lighting consoles (for Lighting) is helpful, but a good sense of focus and teamwork is most important.

**COMPENSATION TYPE:** Volunteer / Possible post-show stipend
*(We want to be transparent: these are volunteer positions, but if funds allow, a small stipend may be available after the production.) *

**DATES & COMMITMENTS:**
* **Rehearsals (for reference):** Sundays, 6–9 PM starting August 3, 2025
Trust Arts Education Center — 807 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA
* **Tech Week:** November 24 – December 3, 2025 (dark day on Thanksgiving)
* **Performances:** December 4–7, 2025 (5 performances total)
Three Stories Theater — 937 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA

We’re happy to work with your schedule — please share any known conflicts when reaching out.

**TO APPLY**
Please email **playboxpgh@gmail.com** with:
* Resume (or a brief note on your experience and interest)
* Availability during tech week and performances

If it seems like a good fit, we’ll be in touch right away!

Thank you,
Marc Palombo
**PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS**

items.text:
Hello!

My name is Marc and I am currently an MFA in Cinematic Arts student at Concordia.

I’m putting out a very early casting call for my thesis short film ***Reprendre***. Production is planned for **summer 2026 (Exact Dates TBD)**.

This is a **paid role**, open to both union and non union actors. Whether you’re a professional or a first time actor, you’re welcome to audition. If you don't reside in Montreal, transportation, lodging, and food will be paid.

The posters include all the key details for your reference.

I’m especially interested in talent with piano skills, though this is **not mandatory**. While the film involves piano, its heart centers on intergenerational trauma, masculinity, and healing.

Please feel free to email me if you have any questions or concerns!

In your submission, indicate your level of bilingualism in French and English (e.g., basic, conversational, fluent, or native). Please also indicate your level of piano proficieney, using the following scale: novice, beginner, intermediate, advanced, or professional.‎'‎

message.text:
Szukasz wyjątkowej kreacji na wesele, studniówkę lub sesję zdjęciową?

W mojej wypożyczalni znajdziesz sukienki wieczorowe w różnych rozmiarach i stylach – od klasycznej elegancji po nowoczesny glamour.

👗 Każda sukienka jest w doskonałym stanie, przygotowana do założenia od razu.

💐 Możliwość przymiarki w Gdańsku (po wcześniejszym umówieniu).

🧼 W cenie: czyszczenie po wypożyczeniu.

Zajrzyj na mój profil 

📸ig @luksusowe_kiecki_wynajem

 by zobaczyć aktualne modele i nowości!

📍Gdańsk – ul.Borkowska 

📩 Napisz , chętnie doradzę, co będzie najlepsze na Twoją okazję.

#sukienkigdansk #wypożyczalniasukienek #studniówka2025 #wesele2025 #elegancjawnajem

items.text:
**STATYŚCI - ŁÓDŹ - SERIAL**

Na kilka większych planów zdjęciowych szukamy statystów:
* **Mężczyźni i kobiety **w różnym wieku 20-80 lat - panowie ogoleni na gładko, bez nowoczesnych fryzur, mocno wygolonych boków itp.; kobiety - bez sztucznych rzęs, widocznych operacji, hybryd itp.

**Stawka: **120 zł - gotówka po planie.

**Gdzie: **Łódź.

**Kiedy: **20.10, 21.10 i 22.10.

***Można zgłaszać się na kilka dat. Tam, gdzie mogę, postaram się powtarzać te same osoby przez kilka dni.**

***Osoby, które do tej pory się zgłosiły, nadal są brane pod uwagę.**

**Zgłoszenia **proszę wysyłać na adres: LDZ.STATYSCI@GMAIL.COM

w treści podając:

imię i nazwisko,

wiek,

miasto,

numer kontaktowy,

wybrane daty,

aktualne zdjęcia,

**W tytule: "Łódź - statysta/ka".**

items.text:
**UKRYTA PRAWDA  - WARSZAWA LISTOPAD**

Poszukuję osób do poniższych ról, wybrani zostaną zaproszeni na casting ONLINE z reżyserką w niedzielę (19.10):

1. **PAULINA (43-48 lat)** - fryzjerka, zadbana, z klasą. Materialistka o dość pragmatycznym podejściu do życia. 
* 3-5.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 600 zł 

1. **SEKRETARKA (30-40 lat)** - elegancka, seksowna, pełen makijaż, może być mało naturalna. 
* 3-5.11 (jeden dzień z tego przedziału), stawka 350 zł 

1. **ADAM (17-20 lat) **-  szczupły, jeszcze dziecięca uroda, nikły zarost. 
* 5-7.11, stawka 1200 zł 

📩 Mailowo proszę przesłać informacje: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, numer telefonu oraz materiały: wideo wizytówkę, aktualne zdjęcia i informacje o doświadczeniu. 

Zgłoszenia kierujemy na: [patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl](mailto:patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl) w tytule wpisując nazwę roli.

items.text:
**WARSAW **

**October 29th or 30th **

**(availability required on both days)**

**Rate: PLN 1200 per day**

For a **commercial for the DISPLATE brand**, a manufacturer of metal posters, I am looking for people of **various ethnic backgrounds** **as Black people, Asian etc.**

Physically attractive, with nice smiles and facial expressions. 

***Please attach your videocard / showreel as a YouTube link*** *– a short video where you talk about yourself, max 40 sec.*

Exploitation fields: Internet 

APPLY to: **ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl**
Subject: **DISPLATE**
In the body: full name, age, phone number, city of residence, and nationality.
Attached: CURRENT photo of face and full figure. 

Portrait photo of face, in daylight, straight on, looking into the lens. Without any filters. Without glasses. Without head covering

items.text:
Title: Forever Home

Genre: Horror/Thriller

Logline: A young couple tours their dream home with an unsettling real estate agent, only to discover the house holds a dark secret.

Roles:

-Raymond Russo

Age: 45-60

Gender: Male

Ethnicity: White

Description: A veteran real estate agent with a polished exterior. He is charming, articulate, and seemingly trustworthy. Beneath the polished exterior, however, is something deeply unsettling.

Requirements: Actor must be skilled with subtle menace and controlled delivery. Suited look; sharp features a plus.

-Susan

Age: 25-35

Gender: Female

Ethnicity: Any

Description: An optimistic, curious young woman who’s excited about starting a new chapter with her husband. She’s practical yet impulsive when her curiosity is piqued.

Requirements: Needs range from natural warmth to terror. Must handle emotional intensity and physical acting in horror scenes.

Production Type: Indie

Contact Information: [luke@lostefilms.com](mailto:luke@lostefilms.com)

Run Time: Short

Compensation: Paid

Union Status: Non-union

Audition Information: Please email headshot, resume and demo reel to email provided (luke@lostefilms.com). We will send a copy of the script and audition instructions.

Shooting Schedule: One short shoot day must happen as soon as possible to capture the brief exterior scenes before leaves are all gone. The other full shoot day will be scheduled close to the exterior shoot day.

Filming Location: Denver metro area

Looking forward to your submissions!

items.text:
CU DENVER STUDENT FILM CASTING CALL

Title: *Mannequins*

Genre: Thriller/Horror

Written and Directed by Archer Beck

Produced by Owen Etter

Logline: In a world where otherworldly invaders have forced humanity to live out a sitcom for their entertainment, the daughter figure in a mismatched family of strangers attempts to escape from her lifelong suburban prison.

Synopsis: In a carefully manufactured sitcom world, Daughter begins to see cracks in the illusion of her perfect family life. While she dreams of escaping the endless loop of canned laughter and staged dinners, Father insists they obey their unseen creators and preserve the family’s image at all costs. Their clash escalates into open rebellion—until Mother, torn between them, helps Daughter break free. Outside the safety of their household, however, Daughter discovers a world ruled by an even stranger, otherworldly power—and must decide whether freedom is worth the price of losing the only family she’s ever known.

Main Roles: 

**Daughter **(16-18): Eldest daughter figure who is hellbent on escaping and finding answers.

**Father **(40s): Head of the household who is trying to keep the family unit obedient to the alien conquerors that control them.

**Mother **(40s): Silent caretaker of the family.

**Son **(8-10): Golden child of the household.

Union Status: Non-Union

Production Type: Student Short Film

Runtime: 10-12 minutes

Compensation: Meals Provided, Any Transportation Fees Paid For, Film & IMDb Credit, Copy of Final Cut

Location: Denver Area

Submission Details:

To submit for audition, please send headshot(s), resumé, and reel (if available) to owen.etter@ucdenver.edu.

Hi everyone, quick update to make the group more useful and less noisy 🎭

We’re introducing **Pre-Approval for Posting** for trusted industry professionals who post opportunities, services, classes and castings. If you’re an Acting Coach, Theatre, Headshot Photographer, Casting Agency, Agent, Director, Producer or similar, you can apply for pre-approval so your posts skip the approval queue.

If you’d like to be pre-approved, please fill in this short form: https://forms.gle/6MkgwGQj8sEh6QEj9

Why apply? 

Pre-approved posters have their posts published instantly (no waiting), get a small “Approved Pro” flair in the group, and help keep the feed relevant for actors.

Who we’ll consider: Acting Coaches, Drama Schools, Theatres, Headshot Photographers (headshot-specific), Casting Agencies, Agents, Directors, Producers, and other verified industry services.

We’ll review each application within 3–5 business days. 

Please only apply if you’re legitimately offering industry-related services. Spammy or low-quality promo will be declined.

Any questions, drop them below and we’ll answer. Thanks for helping keep this group professional and useful 🙏

ATTENTION, FILMMAKERS! 🎬 Don't miss this opportunity at BBR INDIE FILMS!

​We are honored to feature Dwayne Boyd as our celebrity guest panelist! Dwayne is a CEO, a respected Acting Coach, and the founder of Premier Actors Network (PAN).

​Mr. Boyd's expertise is invaluable for filmmakers looking to elevate their projects. He's also been seen in major productions like The Hunger Games, Kingdom Business, and Nashville to name a few.

🎯 Filmmakers: Learn his secrets to getting cast, directing actors, and professional packaging. This is your chance to gain a competitive edge!

​🎃 BEST COSTUME WINS A PRIZE!

​OCT 29th | 6 PM | Studio Movie Grill. Marietta.

Tickets are selling fast: www.bbrindiefilms.com, or Eventbrite.com

ATTENTION, FILMMAKERS! 🎬 Don't miss this opportunity at BBR INDIE FILMS!

​We are honored to feature Dwayne Boyd as our celebrity guest panelist! Dwayne is a CEO, a respected Acting Coach, and the founder of Premier Actors Network (PAN).

​Mr. Boyd's expertise is invaluable for filmmakers looking to elevate their projects. He's also been seen in major productions like The Hunger Games, Kingdom Business, and Nashville to name a few.

🎯 Filmmakers: Learn his secrets to getting cast, directing actors, and professional packaging. This is your chance to gain a competitive edge!

​🎃 BEST COSTUME WINS A PRIZE!

​OCT 29th | 6 PM | Studio Movie Grill. Marietta.

Tickets are selling fast: www.bbrindiefilms.com, or Eventbrite.com

sharedPost.text:
💥 Character Spotlight: Luther Biggs 💥

Today we spotlight Tobias Armand who embodies the ruthless and unstoppable Luther Biggs — the kingpin of Philly. 💼💣
Luther takes no BS from anyone. He’s cutthroat, calculated, and runs the streets with an iron fist. Nothing moves in the city without him knowing it. 

But there’s one person bold enough to stand in his way — Detective Simone Wyatt. And she’s determined to bring him down by any means necessary. 🔥

The tension is real. The action is explosive. The showdown? Unforgettable.

🎬 Don’t miss the WORLD PREMIERE of Bullet Rush —
📅 This Sunday, October 19, 2025
📍 The Plaza Theatre – Atlanta, GA

🎟 Tickets are still on sale but going fast! Get yours now and be part of the rush!

items.text:
Hi everyone! We’re filming a short home video–style flashback scene for our upcoming film Feel the Burn and are looking for a few performers to join us.

Roles:

 • Girl (ages 5–10) – Caucasian

 • Boy (ages 5–10) – Black / African Canadian

 • Mother (ages 30–40) – Caucasian, preferably blonde, to play the girl’s mom

The scene will be shot to resemble nostalgic camcorder footage, capturing a warm and natural family moment.

Details:

 • Shoot Duration: Approximately 2 hours

 • Compensation: $75 per actor

 • Location: Metro Vancouver 

If you or someone you know fits the description and is interested, please send a recent photo and your contact info to feeltheburnmovie@gmail.com.

We welcome submissions from both professional and first-time performers!

topComments.text: Hi Jasper! Do you know when the filming dates are?
The dates will be decided once we have a cast

If you or someone you know fits the description and is interested, please send a recent photo and your contact info to feeltheburnmovie@gmail.com.

We welcome submissions from both professional and first-time performers!

📹 Videographer Needed – San Jose, CA – $250

Looking for a videographer in the San Jose, California area to film a short interview session.

Details:

You must be able to shoot video and record clean audio

The interview will be conducted via Zoom (I will handle the questions remotely)

The actual interview should take no more than one hour, plus setup and breakdown time

Total Pay: $250

Requirements:

Bring your own camera and audio gear

Experience filming interviews is a plus

Professional and punctual

To Apply: Please send:

A link to your work/portfolio

Your contact information

Thank you, Joe

items.text:
1)           Andrzej Rybnicki vel Łukasz Chmielowiec (38) – dobrze zbudowany, silny i wysportowany. Brutalny przestępca, który kiedyś kierował grupą przestępczą, obecnie prowadzi przykładne życie u boku rodziny, prowadząc dobrze prosperującą firmę handlową. Lekko paranoidalny – cały czas boi się, że jego konkurenci z przeszłości go odnajdą i skrzywdzą jego rodzinę. 

 

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 450 zł netto

 

  

2)           Mateusz Grzesiak (19) – uczeń ostatniej klasy technikum. Zgodził się pomóc w napadzie, licząc, że sporo na tym zarobi. 

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 450 zł netto 

 

3)           Paweł Grzesiak (47) – mąż Iwony, schludnie ubrany, pracuje w korporacji. Przyjeżdża, aby być przy żonie podczas identyfikacji zwłok.

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 250 zł netto

4)           Policjant z drogówki (30) – ojciec 2 dzieci, próbuje reanimować Nikodema. 

Data: 04 listopada

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

5)           Nikodem Wolski (19) –  „Młody i głupi”, zaplanował napad, zachciało mu się łatwej kasy. 

Data: 04 i 05 listopada

Stawka: 400 zł netto za całość

Chętnych Panów zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:

1.           Wiek/wzrost/waga

2.           Nr tel. Do kontaktu

3.           Krótki opis doświadczenia

4.           Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe

5.           Aktualne zdjęcie

6.           Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

**DREAM. TEACH. INSPIRE. JOIN OUR BIRMINGHAM TEAM! 🌟**

 

Dance&Arts is thrilled to be growing, and we're looking for passionate **teachers** to join our team right here in **Birmingham**! If you love inspiring young children (aged 4-16) through creative and performing arts, we want to hear from you!

 

We're seeking instructors for a variety of classes. Do you teach any of these styles?

 

✅ **Dance (all styles)**

✅ **Drama**

✅ **Musical Theatre**

✅ **Basic Gymnastics (mat-based only)**

✅ **Arts & Crafts**

 

**💰 Great Pay:** We offer **£30 per hour**.

 

**IMPORTANT DBS REQUIREMENT**

Applicants must have a valid **Enhanced DBS**, or must be **willing to obtain one**. If you need to apply for one, **we will happily provide you with guidelines **for the process!

 

**📩 How to Apply:** Send your valid **Enhanced DBS and CV** to **admin@dancearts-uk.com**.

 

***Crucially, please include the position you are applying for and the location in the subject line of your email (e.g., Dance Teacher - Birmingham).***

 

Join us in bringing creativity, movement, and inspiration to the next generation in Birmingham!

 

We're also seeking instructors in **London, Nottingham, and Manchester**!

#JobOpportunity #BirminghamJobs #HiringTeachers #DanceAndArts #TeachingJobs #PerformingArts #CreativeEducation #Birmingham

The Casper Black Casting team are currently seeking participants for a groundbreaking new reality game show for a major broadcaster... 🎥 📺

Does your job or lifestyle surprise people? Do you have opinions that other people wouldn't expect you to?

We are looking for people from all walks of life. The** bold, **the **authentic** and the **outspoken**.  

*This is no ordinary reality show.*

Email today to receive a short application form:

casting@casperblackcasting.com

**Don't miss out, this could be the best thing you do all year. **

You must be based in the UK to be considered. Over 18s only. 

*For details on how we handle and protect your personal information, please view our full Privacy Policy: *https://www.casperblackcasting.com/privacy-policy

We wanted to let you know about two exciting opportunities coming up at Red Players Academy in Manchester – perfect for young performers aged 9+

🔥 1. October Half-Term Drama & Acting Course (Ages 10-17)

Join us for three full days of elite performance training this October!

📅 Mon 27th – Wed 29th Oct 

🎬Course designed by Lee Battle – TV actor & performance academic (Coronation Street, Casualty, Robin Hood)

 🎉2. FREE Drama Workshop – Launching New Saturday Classes!

Come and try our brand-new Saturday drama classes for FREE!

📅 Saturday 1st November 2025

🎬 Open to young performers aged 9+

📣 Our students are currently appearing in:

📺 Netflix’s Adolescence

⚽ CBBC’s Jamie Johnson FC

🎭 13 Going on 30 @ Manchester Opera House

🔍 CBBC’s Odd Squad

…and more!

🎭 Explore Acting for Stage & Screen

🎓 Taught by expert acting coaches with real industry experience

🌟 Opportunity to be considered for our SPOTLIGHT registered Talent Agency

📍 Altrincham venue | ⏰ Limited spaces – book now!

🌟Ready to join us?

👉 www.redplayersacademy.com/courses

If you have any questions or want to reserve a spot send us a Facebook message or contact us on:

📱 07441 396970

📧 info@redplayers.co.uk

We’d love to see you there!

— The RPA Team 🎭

**Members of this FB group may use the code FB15 for an additional 15% off!**

⚡️PAY WHAT YOU CAN showreel editing service⚡️

Happy Friday all! 

I'm providing a showreel service for new or established actors/directors/cinematographers/comedians/hobbyists etc 

I'm an actor myself so I know how frustrating it can be, especially when you're starting out, to collate your footage together to get more work, without wanting to spend a fortune. 

Basically, send me your footage (or I can try and source it for you if it's commercially aired) and I shall edit it together into a lovely reel. Please see samples in the link below. 

As I'm wanting to add to my portfolio it will be PAY WHAT YOU CAN 

I'll look forward to hearing from you:
reelsforanyone@gmail.com 

Thanks!

🎬 Hey zusammen!

Ich bin David, 55 Jahre alt aus Frankfurt am Main.
Ich bin 1,80 m groß, sportlich gebaut und vom Typ her eher südländisch & modern.

Ich habe zwar noch keine Filmerfahrung, aber richtig Lust, vor der Kamera zu stehen und in verschiedene Rollen zu schlüpfen – ob als Statist, Kleindarsteller oder für kleinere Szenen.

Ich bin zuverlässig, offen und bringe gute Laune mit 😊
Wenn jemand ein Casting in Frankfurt oder Umgebung anbietet oder Statisten sucht, freue ich mich sehr über eine Nachricht!

📧 Kontakt: teppichzentrum14@gmail.com

Liebe Grüße
Dieter

items.text:
🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

topComments.text: Habe auch per WhatsApp die Person kontaktiert
Habe geschrieben!

👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

items.text:
Mangler i en sjov aktivitet i efterårsferien, så søger vi statister til videooptagelse på Gammelbro Camping i Haderslev.

Vi leder efter et par (alder 25-45år), som skal medvirke i en kort reklamefilm.

Vi skal filme stemningsfulde øjeblikke som gåture langs vandet, afslapning i en hytte med kaffe og brætspil. 

Optagelserne varer et par timer, og du/I vil få et gavekort som tak for hjælpen.

Dato: 14. eller 15. okt. - klokkeslæt aftales ved henvendelse.

Sted: Gammelbro Camping reception, Årøsund.

Lyder det som jer?

Send en kort besked og et billede til casting@flowerhaus.dk 

– så vender vi hurtigt tilbage

attachments.ocrText: Kan være et billede af sky, natur, strand og ocean

items.text:
This is me (and Zoe), ten years into a journey that almost never started.

At 47, after a 16-year break, I tried to relaunch my acting career in Germany with no reel, no contacts, and very rusty skills. I had no idea how to explain the gap on my resume, and the thought of walking into a casting room again terrified me.

But giving up was not an option.

The solution hit me when I realized the problem itself was pointing the way forward. I needed training in English at a high level, and it did not exist in Munich. Flying to London, LA, or New York was unrealistic.

So I organized the workshops myself.

What happened next changed everything.

Instead of stumbling around in the dark trying to figure it out again, I could hit the ground running. Whenever I needed something like showreel material, headshots, the right kind of training, I organized it and got what I needed. If I had tried to piece it all together on my own, it would have taken ten times as long, and I did not have that kind of time.

That approach became my foundation. It is what eventually opened doors to work with studios like A24, Netflix, and Hallmark.

Along the way, I got world-class training for free as the organizer. A community of actors formed around those workshops. And unexpectedly, it also turned into steady income.

Here is the breakthrough: I always believed you had to "make it" before you could make money as a creative. What I discovered is that the journey itself can pay for itself.

Use what you need, whether that is training, practice, connections, or visibility, and shape it into something that lets other people get what they need too. That way you move your craft forward, build real relationships, get seen, and the process funds itself.

At first, I thought this only worked for actors because that is where I started. But the more I shared my story, the more I heard the same frustrations from other creatives: photographers, writers, artisans, even people into things like fermentation or traditional crafts. That's when it clicked. This approach is not just about acting. It can work anywhere someone is willing to use what they need to build what they want.

Ten years later, I am still living this way. I am constantly building skills, deepening connections, getting more visible in my craft, and funding it all as I go.

I am sharing this because I know too many people who keep their passions in the "someday" box. They wait until they feel "ready" or "expert enough" before letting themselves imagine it could actually support them.

But what if the very thing you think is holding you back is actually your starting point to a creative life that fits?

👉 For me, it was not having reel material or training. What’s been that thing for you?

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of dog

topComments.text: The competitive nature of the wider job market really dictates that people choose talent over passion. When you are good at something, it is easier to become passionate about it. This is true for creative artists as much as anyone on any career path.

items.text:
Hi all,

Does anyone know whether it is still possible for international students at the moment to get a film internship? I would be looking for Fall 2026 (I know it's in a long time but I prefer to prepare myself ahead), but when looking up at some of the internship opportunities, some of them state that they won't accept students with an F1/J1 visa (which used to work for interns too).

items.text:
Do you have a passion for all things scary?

A walk that sends shivers down spines?

Or maybe you just love being part of the chaos behind the scares?

Fear Columbus in Columbus, Ohio  is HIRING IMMEDIATELY for:

🩸 Haunted House Actors (unleash your inner monster, clown, or demon)

🩸 Event Staff (keep the terror running smoothly from the shadows)

✨ No experience? No problem. We’ll train you to scare like a pro.

✨ evening shifts + the most fun job you’ll ever have.

✨ Be part of one of the largest haunted attractions in Ohio.

This is your chance to join our spooky family and create memories (and nightmares) that guests won’t forget!

💀 Apply NOW and come be a part of all the spooky fun! 

⚡ Don’t wait — the screams start soon and spots are filling FAST! 

Click the link below or in my bio for info on what it entails working here and for the application! 

Can't wait to see you <3

[https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/](https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/)

CASTING CALL - SUPPORTING CHARACTERS - DUALITY: THE SERIES

We are on the lookout for actors who are interested in taking part for our 4 part limited series.

DUALITY: THE SERIES is a 4 part coming of age teen drama limited series that explores the lives of 4 teenagers in different stages of their lives, this series explores themes of friendship, identity,

If you are interested READ CAREFULLY!!

items.text:
**Are you looking for a drama academy that prepares you for a career as an actor in film, Theatre, or TV?**

Then you can look no further than Marble Academy in Swinton, Manchester.

 

**Why Choose Marble Academy?**

Recognised by Spotlight as an academy of renowned excellence and winner of the **Manchester & North West Prestige Awards for**
**Drama School of the Year,** you'll receive authentic training from one of the best.
Our inspiring, award-winning tutor, Christian Le Feuvre, will help you unlock your potential, boost your confidence, help you improve the talent you have to get you where you want to
be in your career as an actor, and ultimately capture the attention of castingdirectors.

 

At Marble Academy, it’s not just about our classes; we create award-winning films, host workshops and provide casting opportunities for our students.

Explore our glowing reviews, learn about our
classes, and book your audition at: www.marbleacademy.co.uk.

 

**DON'T BE AN ACTOR BECAUSE YOU WANT TO;**
**BE AN ACTOR BECAUSE YOU 'HAVE' TO!**

items.text:
Have you ever wondered why some people simply fill the room the moment they walk in?
It’s not magic — it’s presence. And it’s something you can actually train.
In this one-afternoon creative space, we explore presence and expression through psychological and theatre-based exercises. You’ll learn how to connect more deeply with your body, attention, and authenticity — whether you’re on stage, teaching, performing, or simply engaging with others in everyday life.

sharedPost.text:
🎬 The Foundry Acting Studio…. Where Real Actors Are Made

Have you ever wanted to be an actor, but people told you it was impossible?
Maybe they laughed. Maybe they said, “Yeah right, you’ll be on TV one day.”
Maybe you believed them.

The truth is, it is possible. And we’re proving it every single day.

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we’ve taken people from call centres, factories, construction sites and put them on real film sets. We’ve helped ordinary people create extraordinary careers.

Because when you train with us, you’re not just joining another acting class, you’re stepping into a professional studio that’s already earned the highest recognition possible:

✨ SPOTLIGHT APPROVED – our curriculum exceeds the UK’s highest acting standard by over three times.
🌍 SAG RECOGNISED – the same union that represents every Hollywood star on earth.
🎥 FILM-FOCUSED TRAINING – you don’t just practice scenes; you act in real films. Short films, features, festival submissions, full productions we make them all in-house, to professional industry standard.

And all of this — for just £100 every 4 weeks (£80 for teens).
No false promises. No city centre price tags. Just real, legitimate training and real results.

We believe acting shouldn’t be locked behind London doors.
That’s why we’re bringing professional-level training to Yorkshire and the North, so anyone with the passion to perform can do it, whether you’re 16 or 60, starting fresh or chasing the dream you left behind.

🎭 Because the truth is: there is no other independent studio in the UK that offers what we do.
We’re Spotlight approved.
We’re SAG recognised.
We make films.
We get results.

You don’t get more legitimate than that.
You just don’t.

So, if you’re ready to stop wondering “what if” and start actually doing it, this is your moment.

🔥 SPOTLIGHT APPROVED. SAG RECOGNISED. FILM FOCUSED.
The Foundry Acting Studio….
Where impossible dreams get rehearsed, filmed, and released.

🎬 Adult & Teen Classes | 🎭 Limited Places | 🌍 Open Across Yorkshire & The North
👉 Message us now to reserve your place.

items.text:
****🎉 ONLY A WEEK TO GO! ** **

 

Get ready for the Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event happening on Sunday, 26th October! 

 

****📍 Location:** **HOME Mcr**, 2 Tony Wilson Pl, Manchester M15 4FN **

****🕑 Time:** 2:00 p.m. - 6:30 p.m. **

 

This is not just another event; it’s your chance to connect with a dynamic community of actors, directors, producers, and writers who share your passion!
Networking is an essential part of our industry, so don’t let this opportunity pass you by.
Tickets are available at this link. 

[https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239](https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239)

 

Get ready to immerse yourself in a space filled with talented actors, visionary directors, influential producers, and skilled crew members, all eager to forge meaningful connections and who could help bring your next big project to life.

 

Also, if you're looking for captivating headshots or seeking to refresh your current images, the excellent Lisa Barton from Lisa Barton photography will be joining us at the event to showcase her incredible work!
Don’t miss out—make sure to stop by and connect with her!

 

Come and join us, we can’t wait to meet you 🌟

-First & Last Name

-Email Address

**UKRYTA PRAWDA  - WARSZAWA LISTOPAD**

Poszukuję osób do poniższych ról, wybrani zostaną zaproszeni na casting ONLINE z reżyserką w niedzielę (19.10):

1. **KAMILA (42-48 lat)** - ładna, zgrabna, kobieca, sympatyczna. Na co dzień ma spokojną pracę w administracji metra i jest częściej w domu niż zapracowany Piotr. **ROLA GŁÓWNA KONIECZNE DOŚWIADCZENIE!**
* 5-7.11, stawka 1800 zł 

1. MARIUSZ (44-50 lat) - tatusiowaty, z brzuszkiem, kierownik na stacji benzynowej. 
* 5-7.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 800 zł 

1. **PAULINA (43-48 lat)** - fryzjerka, zadbana, z klasą. Materialistka o dość pragmatycznym podejściu do życia. 
* 3-5.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 600 zł 

1. **SEKRETARKA (30-40 lat)** - elegancka, seksowna, pełen makijaż, może być mało naturalna. 
* 3-5.11 (jeden dzień z tego przedziału), stawka 350 zł

1. **KAMILA (42-48 lat)** - ładna, zgrabna, kobieca, sympatyczna. Na co dzień ma spokojną pracę w administracji metra i jest częściej w domu niż zapracowany Piotr. **ROLA GŁÓWNA KONIECZNE DOŚWIADCZENIE!**
* 5-7.11, stawka 1800 zł 

1. MARIUSZ (44-50 lat) - tatusiowaty, z brzuszkiem, kierownik na stacji benzynowej. 
* 5-7.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 800 zł 

1. **PAULINA (43-48 lat)** - fryzjerka, zadbana, z klasą. Materialistka o dość pragmatycznym podejściu do życia. 
* 3-5.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 600 zł 

1. **SEKRETARKA (30-40 lat)** - elegancka, seksowna, pełen makijaż, może być mało naturalna. 
* 3-5.11 (jeden dzień z tego przedziału), stawka 350 zł 

📩 Mailowo proszę przesłać informacje: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, numer telefonu oraz materiały: wideo wizytówkę, aktualne zdjęcia i informacje o doświadczeniu. 

Zgłoszenia kierujemy na: [patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl](mailto:patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl) w tytule wpisując nazwę roli.

sharedPost.text:
1)           Andrzej Rybnicki vel Łukasz Chmielowiec (38) – dobrze zbudowany, silny i wysportowany. Brutalny przestępca, który kiedyś kierował grupą przestępczą, obecnie prowadzi przykładne życie u boku rodziny, prowadząc dobrze prosperującą firmę handlową. Lekko paranoidalny – cały czas boi się, że jego konkurenci z przeszłości go odnajdą i skrzywdzą jego rodzinę. 

 

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 450 zł netto

 

  

2)           Mateusz Grzesiak (19) – uczeń ostatniej klasy technikum. Zgodził się pomóc w napadzie, licząc, że sporo na tym zarobi. 

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 450 zł netto 

 

3)           Paweł Grzesiak (47) – mąż Iwony, schludnie ubrany, pracuje w korporacji. Przyjeżdża, aby być przy żonie podczas identyfikacji zwłok.

Data: 05 listopada

Stawka: 250 zł netto

4)           Policjant z drogówki (30) – ojciec 2 dzieci, próbuje reanimować Nikodema. 

Data: 04 listopada

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

5)           Nikodem Wolski (19) –  „Młody i głupi”, zaplanował napad, zachciało mu się łatwej kasy. 

Data: 04 i 05 listopada

Stawka: 400 zł netto za całość

Chętnych Panów zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:

1.           Wiek/wzrost/waga

2.           Nr tel. Do kontaktu

3.           Krótki opis doświadczenia

4.           Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe

5.           Aktualne zdjęcie

6.           Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

**Poszukiwani statyści i statystki do programu TV – Katowice!**

Do udziału w nagraniach programu telewizyjnego poszukujemy statystów i statystek w różnym wieku, z wysportowaną sylwetką.
Lokalizacja: Katowice
Data nagrania: 21 października do godz. 15:00

Osoby zainteresowane prosimy o zgłoszenie się w wiadomości prywatnej – koniecznie podaj numer telefonu.

items.text:
Aqui Yused Samir Leon  Artista de circo tradicional de colombia 
#lionbrothersofficial #samirichy #circuslife #circusshow #colombianosenmelbourne #mindset #desarrollopersonal
Trabaja tu físico porque tu cuerpo es tu carta de presentación ante el mundo. Es el reflejo visible de tu disciplina, tu respeto por ti mismo y tu capacidad de imponerte al confort. Un cuerpo fuerte grita autoridad, determinación y autocontrol. Un cuerpo débil, en cambio, revela desorden y abandono. No se trata de estética, se trata de energía. Quien se domina físicamente, se domina mentalmente

items.text:
Mickey Mouse Horror Short Film
Hello, I am currently producing a Mickey Mouse Short film, with the working title, The Mouse Killer, which may become the actual title. 

This film is apart of my two existing films, My Horrible Roommate Winnie The Pooh 1 and 2. This serves as the next chapter within the series, that will lead into the 3rd and final My Horrible Roommate Winnie The Pooh film. 

Film Synopsis: two women are out in the woods, hunting down a mythical creature known as, Steamboat Willie, or Willie. 

If it all works out, this short film will be the start of a trilogy of short films. With the final one leading up to My Horrible Roommate Winnie The Pooh 3.

Actors Age Range: 21 to up.

Looking for two females who can play the roles.

Compensation: none

Location: Fort Collins Colorado 

If you're interested, send me a message!

items.text:
🎥** PAID CASTING CALL**

We are casting several roles for a series of short narrative pieces that highlight the stories of real families supported by our organization. These stories portray authenticity, warmth, and emotional depth.

**Location:** East Vancouver
**Audition Date:** October 20th

**Shooting Date:** October 23rd; must be available from 10-4 (you will not be needed the entire day)
**Compensation:** $200

**We are looking for actresses/actors to play: **

**Bruna**
* Female, late 20s to mid-40s
* Mother; caring and loving. Must convey determination, worry, and hope while navigating financial and emotional challenges for her children.

**Aisha**
* Female, early 30s to mid-40s
* Mother; warm, exhausted, and hopeful. Portrays a single parent managing multiple responsibilities with love and perseverance.

**Steven**
* Male, early 30s to mid-50s
* Father; provides care and guidance amid family hardship. Able to convey emotional strength and compassion.

**David**
* Male, mid-30s to 50s
* Father; supportive, patient, and empathetic. Represents the emotional toll of parenting through challenges while remaining steadfast for his family.

Please send a brief introduction and your headshot to **communications@ldsociety.ca. **We encourage applicants of all ethnicities and gender identities to apply.

Following auditions, we will confirm if you got the role and your timeslot via email on Tuesday, October 21st.

Jeg søger statister til at medvirke i lidt video i Støvring/Svenstrup nu på onsdag den 15. oktober.

𝗛𝘃𝗲𝗺 𝘀ø𝗴𝗲𝗿 𝗷𝗲𝗴:

Jeg søger to "familier". 

Familie 1: En mand og en kvinde, der kan passe til en børnefamilie. Hertil også en-to børn. 

Familie 2: Et mere "modent" par (mand og kvinde) samt en eventuel hund.

OBS! Ingen store, synlige tatoveringer eller lignende. 

𝗣𝗿𝗮𝗸𝘁𝗶𝘀𝗸 𝗶𝗻𝗳𝗼: 
📍 Optagelserne foregår i Svenstrup og Støvring. 

🗓️ Onsdag den 15. oktober. Enten kl. 9.30-12.00 eller 13.00-15.00. Det aftales nærmere.

💸 Jobbet betales med gavekort på 500 kr. pr mand. 

Optagelserne skal bruges til annoncering på Metas samt andre digitale platforme til et typehusfirma. Der er tale om flere klip af et hverdagsliv i et af vores udstillingshuse.

items.text:
Projekt: Kurzfilm „Zwischen Schatten und Licht“

Drehzeit: Januar 2026

Ort: Umkreis von 200 km von Nordhorn 

Format: Kurzfilm

Gesuchte Rollen:

1️⃣ Lucy

 • Spielalter: 26

 • Charakter: Nett, liebevoll, beste Freundin von Stella, loyal und immer unterstützend

 • Schauspielerfahrung von Vorteil aber kein Muss . Newcomer sind ebenso herzlich willkommen 

2️⃣ Nick

 • Spielalter: 25

 • Charakter: Gut aussehend, charismatisch, charmant, Sunnyboy

 • Natürliches, sympathisches Spiel erforderlich

⸻

3️⃣ Felix 

• Spielalter :20

Charakter: ehemaliger Drogemjunkie,Stellas jüngerer Bruder, Geldprobleme 

• Schauspielerfahrungen von Vorteil ,gefragtes Spiel erforderlich 

Story / Kurzbeschreibung:

„Zwischen Schatten und Licht“ erzählt die Geschichte von Stella, die unvermittelt in Gefahr gerät: Victor, dem ihr Bruder Geld aus einem Drogendeal schuldet, lauert ihr auf. Als Stella Nick, einen charismatischen jungen Mann, kennenlernt, funkt es zwischen den beiden — nach einem fast stattgefundenen Kuss stürmt Stella jedoch weg und gerät direkt in die Arme des Bösewichts Victor. Nick beobachtet die Situation und kommt gerade rechtzeitig, als ein heftiger Konflikt zwischen ihm und Victor eskaliert, der in einer Messerstecherei gipfelt. Eine spannende Geschichte über Gefahr, Anziehung und Vertrauen.

⸻

Bewerbung gerne per PN

 • Foto / Porträt

 • Alter / Spielalter

 • Kurzer Lebenslauf / Schauspielerfahrung

 • Showreel

Film Title: Clouds Have Bridges Too

Production Company: Wishing Tree Creatives

Director: Wanphrang Diengdoh (award-winning filmmaker)

Featuring: Adil Hussain

Location: Private home in Hertford

Shoot Date: Late October/ November (TBC)

Duration: Approx. 1–2 hours

Role & Requirements

Baby of mixed heritage or person of colour

Ideally: light brown skin, dark hair, dark eyes

Age: 12–18 months

The baby will portray the child of an Indian father and a White British mother

Scene involves only shots of the baby sleeping in a cot/bassinet

No outdoor scenes, no demanding or stressful filming — just peaceful, indoor filming in a gentle, quiet home environment

What We Provide & Expect

Paid role for 1–2 hours

Parents/carers must be present at all times — and are warmly welcomed on set

Calm, safe set with full health & safety protocols — baby’s well-being is the top priority

We ensure breaks, a comfortable temperature, and minimal crew

If you have a baby basket or bassinet, let us know — it may be used for the scene

To Apply:

Please email enquiries@wishingtreecreatives.com with:

1️⃣ Baby’s name, age & heritage

2️⃣ A few recent photos (in natural light)

3️⃣ Your contact details & location

4️⃣ Whether you can bring a cot or bassinet

We’re creating something gentle and beautiful — your baby’s comfort and safety will always come first.

Wishing Tree Creatives

#CastingCall #ShortFilm #BabyCasting #UKFilm #ChildSafety #FilmCasting #WishingTreeCreatives

items.text:
📣🎬 CASTING CALL - Short Period Drama 

We are casting for The Stuntman, a 3-minute period drama made as part of our final year at UWE Bristol. The film will be shot in Bristol in the week commencing 10th November 2025 (exact dates TBC). This is a student project, unpaid, but with expenses covered. The film is intended for university showcase and festival submission.

Story:
Set in 1920s Wiltshire, The Stuntman follows Ed Morris, a small-town silent cinema owner fighting to keep his theatre alive as the arrival of sound threatens to change film forever. With his fiancée Alice by his side, Ed stages one last ambitious stunt in the hope of saving his cinema - and their livelihood. A warm yet bittersweet drama about determination, passion and the march of technological change.

Roles:
Ed Morris (Lead, 28)
Charming, intelligent, and hardworking. Outwardly confident, but hiding a quiet desperation as he struggles to keep silent film alive. Needs strong screen presence and subtle emotional depth.

Alice Fardon (Lead, 22–23)
Ed’s fiancée. Feisty, loyal, and practical. She supports his dreams but occasionally shows frustration at his all-consuming determination.

Community Extras
Townsfolk gathering to watch Ed’s big stunt. A mix of ages. Families, workers and individuals. To capture the atmosphere of a 1920s local community.

Apply by: 1st November 2025
To Apply: Please send a headshot, CV (or Spotlight/Mandy link), and any showreel/self-tape to: Scarlet2.Gerry@live.uwe.ac.uk

Please include in email subject: THE STUNTMAN & NAME

## Profils recherchés :

**DES SILHOUETTES :**

**Des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter** :
* un gérant d’aérodrome
* un pilote d’avion de tourisme (licence + certificat médical valide) 3 décollages / atterrissages dans les 90 jours
* Un dessinateur homme (35 – 50 ans) pour une doublure main
* Des jeunes filles (18 – 27 ans)
* Des pêcheurs
* Des agents de sécurité
* Des serveurs et serveuses
* Des policiers et policières
* Des joueurs de basket(18 – 25 ans)
* Des touristes retraités
* Un groupe de passants

**FIGURATION**

**Nantes et alentours : des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter :**
* Des passants  et passantes, des policiers et policières, des joueurs de basket (18 – 25 ans), du public de match de basket, des pom-pom-girls, des clients et clientes de restaurant, bar et club, un DJ et des automobilistes

**A Clisson et alentours :** **des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter :**
* Des clients et clientes ainsi que des familles au restaurant, un jeune couple

**A Pornic et alentours : des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter :**
* Des pêcheurs, des plaisanciers (si possible avec leur propre bateau), un skipper, des passants et passantes, des clients et clientes de restaurant, des clients et clientes d’un camping

**Lieu de tournage** : Nantes, Clisson et Pornic

**Période de tournage** : du 4 novembre au 13 décembre 2025

**Synopsis** :* Dévastée par la disparition soudaine et inexpliquée de son mari, Esther Bazin, capitaine de police, trouve sur sa route deux civils membres du Groupe de Recherche des Disparitions Volontaires (GRDV). La disparition de son mari étant considérée comme volontaire, la police ne peut enquêter. Esther s’associe donc avec cette brigade au profil singulier. Leur mission ? Résoudre des affaires de disparitions volontaires, « ces évaporés » sur lesquels la police ne peut légalement enquêter.*

Non-Union | Paid Roles | Denver Area

We're casting a heartwarming 1970s nostalgia-themed holiday commercial for a property management company.

SHOOT DATE: November 9, 2025
LOCATION: Denver Area, Colorado
SUBMISSION DEADLINE: Friday, October 24th

USAGE: Full buyout

ROLES AVAILABLE:

CHILD (Male, 7-10) - SPEAKING ROLE - $700/day
Lead role! Looking for a talented young actor who can deliver genuine Christmas morning excitement. Must submit reel showing previous work. This is a standout role perfect for your reel!

Casting Call 📣 

Wir suchen die Gesichter für unsere Haupt- und Nebenrollen! Du findest, du passt perfekt zu einer dieser Figuren? Dann melde dich bei uns! Ganz einfach via Mail deine Bewerbung an casting@datingoffline.de senden 📨 

Drehzeitraum wird zwischen dem 24.11 und 05.12 sein (genauere Infos folgen), gedreht wird in Wiesbaden/Frankfurt und Umgebung 🎥

attachments.ocrText: May be a graphic of text that says 'DATING NORMATOR Hue LOVE GEN DATING OFFLINE CASTING ASTING Call ASHORTFILM A SHORT FILM'

May be an image of text that says 'DATING OFFLINE DATING NORMATOR TA LOVE 한1대1한원 GEN LOGLINE: In einer dystopischen Zukunft, in der Menschen sich selbst ständig normieren und optimieren, zerbricht ein junger Mann an seiner Eifersucht und an dem Versuch, sich für die Liebe neu zu formen. COMINGSOON COMING SOON'

May be a graphic of text that says 'DATING NORMATOR DATING OFFLINE LOVE GEN THEMA In einer Welt, in der echte Begegnungen durch digitale Perfektion ersetzt werden, hinterfragt Dating Offline die Grenzen zwischen Realität und Inszenierung. Der Film erzählt von jungen Menschen, die sich in einem System verlieren, das Authentizität verspricht, aber Kontrolle verlangt. In einer futuristisch-kül Gesellschaft, in der Emotionen algorithmisch gesteuert scheinen, wird das Bedürfnis nach Nähe zu einem Risiko Zwischen Rebellion und Anpassung, Verbindung und Entfremdung, entsteht ein Spannungsfeld, das nicht nur das digitale Zeitalter, sondern auch das Menschsein selbst infrage stellt. COMINGSOON COMING SOON'

May be a graphic of one or more people and text that says 'DATING OFFLING A SHORTFILM Hauptrolle MIRA Mira ist empathisch, aufgeschlossen und wirkt wie ein Gegenentwurf zur normierten, technisierten Welt um herum. Sie verkörpert Echtheit und emotionale Tiefe etwas, das in ihrer Gesellschaft selten gewordeni ist. GESUCHT WIRD: Weiblich 22-30 Jahre, Spielalter 25 •Natür licher, alternativer Look Mira ist eine lebendige, aufgeschlossene Frau, die lieber individuell,a als ein Teil der Gesellschafti ist. Bewerbungen bitte an casting@datingoffline.de'

May be a graphic of text that says 'DATING NO O OR DATING OFFLING - A SHORTFILM τν GEN Hauptrolle LIO Lio wirktnach außen angepasst und unscheinbar. Ihm wichtig, was die anderen denken und möchte dazu gehören. Eigentlich igentlich sucht nach etwas Echtem, Das merkt Mira kennenlernt. Seine angepasste, ideelle Fassade bricht, als Eifersucht ihm hochkocht. alser GESUCHT WIRD: •Mãnnlich 20-27 Jahre, Spielalter 23 schlanker, großer Look gut darin, seine Stimme zu verstellen Bewerbungen bitte an casting@datingoffline.de'

items.text:
🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

🎬 The Foundry Acting Studio…. Where Real Actors Are Made

Have you ever wanted to be an actor, but people told you it was impossible?
Maybe they laughed. Maybe they said, “Yeah right, you’ll be on TV one day.”
Maybe you believed them.

The truth is, it is possible. And we’re proving it every single day.

At The Foundry Acting Studio, we’ve taken people from call centres, factories, construction sites and put them on real film sets. We’ve helped ordinary people create extraordinary careers.

Because when you train with us, you’re not just joining another acting class, you’re stepping into a professional studio that’s already earned the highest recognition possible:

✨ SPOTLIGHT APPROVED – our curriculum exceeds the UK’s highest acting standard by over three times.
🌍 SAG RECOGNISED – the same union that represents every Hollywood star on earth.
🎥 FILM-FOCUSED TRAINING – you don’t just practice scenes; you act in real films. Short films, features, festival submissions, full productions we make them all in-house, to professional industry standard.

And all of this — for just £100 every 4 weeks (£80 for teens).
No false promises. No city centre price tags. Just real, legitimate training and real results.

We believe acting shouldn’t be locked behind London doors.
That’s why we’re bringing professional-level training to Yorkshire and the North, so anyone with the passion to perform can do it, whether you’re 16 or 60, starting fresh or chasing the dream you left behind.

🎭 Because the truth is: there is no other independent studio in the UK that offers what we do.
We’re Spotlight approved.
We’re SAG recognised.
We make films.
We get results.

You don’t get more legitimate than that.
You just don’t.

So, if you’re ready to stop wondering “what if” and start actually doing it, this is your moment.

🔥 SPOTLIGHT APPROVED. SAG RECOGNISED. FILM FOCUSED.
The Foundry Acting Studio….
Where impossible dreams get rehearsed, filmed, and released.

🎬 Adult & Teen Classes | 🎭 Limited Places | 🌍 Open Across Yorkshire & The North
👉 Message us now to reserve your place.

MODEL NEEDED FOR SHOOT IN CHESTER 📍
 
We are looking for 1 model for a restaurant photoshoot in Chester on Wednesday 8th October. The photos and videos will be used on the restaurants’ website & social media to showcase the experience of the venue.

Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot:
 
📆 Date: Wednesday 8th October. 
⏰ Time: 12pm-4pm
 
Requirements:
 
-       Age: Between 21-30
-       Female
-       Wearing casual outfit. 
- some playful tiktoks will also be filmed, so you must be comfortable with playful /sassy content (e.g like this: https://www.instagram.com/reel/DI4rOAITfbP/?igsh=MXd6cXFyaWtqdDdpMg==
 
💸 Compensation:
-       We have the budget to offer each model £125 for the few hours. 
- Food & drinks will be provided. 
 
More in-depth briefing will be given to those selected.
 
Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot and we will be in touch via Facebook DMs.

🎬 CASTING CALL – FEATURE FILM: KASIA KILER (ATLANTA, GA)

A feature film written by Jesse Frank is currently casting for supporting roles.

🗓 Submission Deadline: November 15th, 2025
🎥 Production Starts: November 10th, 2026
📍 Filming Location: Atlanta, GA
💰 Pay: $150/day (Non-Union)
🔎 Applicants must be based in Atlanta, GA to be considered for any role.

📖 Synopsis: Kasia Kiler, tormented by nightmares, uncovers her erased past as Lynn Ryder, a CIA agent trained by Argyle Locklar after traumatic experiences. With the help of a friend, she confronts her fragmented memories and targets the blackmailing villain Jack Crevelle, whose secrets include evidence of her own abuse. In a violent rescue mission, they dismantle Jack’s operation, free hostages, and expose his crimes.

📩 HOW TO APPLY:

🎭 Apply for this casting as a Talent PRO member at Actors and Extras with a 1-month FREE trial period.

👉 Visit: [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)
Create your own FREE profile and GET NOTIFIED of castings in your area. 

Join [www.actorsandextras.com](https://www.actorsandextras.com) today!

items.text:
Warszawa 

Zdjęcia 21.10 wtorek! Plan wstępnie od ok 12 do 18. 

Szukamy:

dwóch panów jako strażników więziennych z lat 70 - bez tatuaży, modnych fryzur, ale ogolonych

jeden ze strażników będzie również współwięźniem.

Wiek ok 40 lat bez brzuszków. 

Stawka -100 odbiór gotówki w biurze. 

 Szukam też - człowieka drobnej postury, wzrost 165/170 cm - bez tatuaży (

Wiek ok 45-60 lat. Wyniszczony więzieniem

Wszystkie role są bez tekstu, ale nasz Pan  o tej posturze  165/170 będzie miał jeszcze dodatkowe dni zdjęciowe w grudniu w Warszawie i na Śląsku (łącznie około 4 dni). Dlatego ważne jest, aby to był ten sam człowiek. Oczywiście zapewnimy transport, nocleg i wyżywienie.

Twarz nie ma dla nas takiego znaczenia, bo chodzi głównie o posturę. Chcemy go pokazywać w większości jako samą sylwetkę.

Stawka za dzień zdjęciowy 150 odbiór gotówki w biurze.

Proszę o zgłaszanie się pod numer 797169069

Z dopiskiem więzień lub Pan postury 165-170cm

W sms prosze umieścić imię, nazwisko wiek tel oraz wyraźne zdjęcia. 

Marta 🙂

items.text:
Hej! 

Do reklamy banku szukam  : 

**Szukamy: **

1. **Dziewczyna - stwór** **-rola główna** wiek 18-24 lata - dziewczęca. Intrygująca twarz, mocne spojrzenie. -  - dziewczyna będzie siedziała na stworze (nie może bać się lekkiej wysokości plus musi mieć taką emocjonalność, która pomoże jej wyobrazic sobie stwora). Mile widziane dziewczyny z doświadczeniem w Motion Capture ale nie jest to konieczność. 
2. **Znajomy : chłopak w wieku 18-25 lata - rola epizodyczna ** szukamy charakterystycznych jak i klasycznie pięknych ludzi. Dziwne fryzury, kolczyki, różne kolory włosów etc. 
3. **Znajoma : dziewczyna w wieku 18-25 lata  - rola epizodyczna**  - szukamy charakterystycznych jak i klasycznie pięknych ludzi. Dziwne fryzury, kolczyki, różne kolory włosów etc.
4. **Chłopak jeżdżący konno - wiek 17-27 lat - - rola główna** wyraźne rysy twarzy, da się lubić, zawadiackie spojrzenie, szczupły, może być wysoki ale nie musi. WARUNEK KONIECZNY : musi jeździć konno. W ujęciu będzie siedział na koniu i jeździł konno więc musimy mieć osobę, której koń się nie boi. I która ma doświadczenie. Kwestia bezpieczeństwa na planie. Wiec prosimy o szczerość w tym temacie. 
5. **Dziewczyna w wannie - wiek 18-25 lat - rola główna ** raczej classy niż sassy. Uwaga dziewczyna będzie miała zdjęcia w wannie, wiec prosimy o osoby które będą się dobrze czuły w występowaniu na planie w kostiumie. 

**TERMINY : **

23.10- termin oddania materiałów do godziny 12.00 

27.10 - Recall 

30.10 - przymiarki 

31.10, 04.11, 05.11 - zdjęcia 

**Prawa podeślę na priv wybranym osobom. **

**Stawki: **

**Główni Bohaterowie: **

1500 zł za dzień zdjęciowy 

5000 zł prawa 

Epizody: 

1500 zł dzień zdjęciowy 

3500 zł prawa 

Zgłoszenia proszę wysyłać do 21.10 do godziny 12.00 na adres [slavic.squad.cast@gmail.com](mailto:slavic.squad.cast@gmail.com) 

W tytule e maila proszę wpisac imie i nazwisko + Bank 
1. Imię i nazwisko 
2. Wiek 
3. Numer telefonu 
4. Do jakiej roli się zgłaszasz 
5. Czy masz doświadczenie w jeździe konnej, jeśli tak to jakie 
6. 2-3 aktualne zdjecia

items.text:
**UKRYTA PRAWDA  - WARSZAWA LISTOPAD**

Poszukuję osób do poniższych ról, wybrani zostaną zaproszeni na casting ONLINE z reżyserką w niedzielę (19.10):

1. **KAMILA (42-48 lat)** - ładna, zgrabna, kobieca, sympatyczna. Na co dzień ma spokojną pracę w administracji metra i jest częściej w domu niż zapracowany Piotr. **ROLA GŁÓWNA KONIECZNE DOŚWIADCZENIE!**
* 5-7.11, stawka 1800 zł 

1. MARIUSZ (44-50 lat) - tatusiowaty, z brzuszkiem, kierownik na stacji benzynowej. 
* 5-7.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 800 zł 

1. **PAULINA (43-48 lat)** - fryzjerka, zadbana, z klasą. Materialistka o dość pragmatycznym podejściu do życia. 
* 3-5.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 600 zł 

1. **SEKRETARKA (30-40 lat)** - elegancka, seksowna, pełen makijaż, może być mało naturalna. 
* 3-5.11 (jeden dzień z tego przedziału), stawka 350 zł 

📩 Mailowo proszę przesłać informacje: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, numer telefonu oraz materiały: wideo wizytówkę, aktualne zdjęcia i informacje o doświadczeniu. 

Zgłoszenia kierujemy na: [patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl](mailto:patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl) w tytule wpisując nazwę roli.

Poszukuję osób do poniższych ról, wybrani zostaną zaproszeni na casting ONLINE z reżyserką w niedzielę (19.10):

1. **KAMILA (42-48 lat)** - ładna, zgrabna, kobieca, sympatyczna. Na co dzień ma spokojną pracę w administracji metra i jest częściej w domu niż zapracowany Piotr. **ROLA GŁÓWNA KONIECZNE DOŚWIADCZENIE!**
* 5-7.11, stawka 1800 zł 

1. MARIUSZ (44-50 lat) - tatusiowaty, z brzuszkiem, kierownik na stacji benzynowej. 
* 5-7.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 800 zł 

1. **PAULINA (43-48 lat)** - fryzjerka, zadbana, z klasą. Materialistka o dość pragmatycznym podejściu do życia. 
* 3-5.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 600 zł 

1. **SEKRETARKA (30-40 lat)** - elegancka, seksowna, pełen makijaż, może być mało naturalna. 
* 3-5.11 (jeden dzień z tego przedziału), stawka 350 zł 

📩 Mailowo proszę przesłać informacje: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, numer telefonu oraz materiały: wideo wizytówkę, aktualne zdjęcia i informacje o doświadczeniu. 

Zgłoszenia kierujemy na: [patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl](mailto:patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl) w tytule wpisując nazwę roli.
